    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> <i>Brothers, Snakes, Fists!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brawl your way from the outskirts of town to the mean streets of Morbat City.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Snakes with Fists</strong> is a retro-inspired Beat ’em Up / RPG hybrid. Battle through replayable stages, level up your character, and unlock new abilities as you go. Explore an open map, uncover challenges, and prove yourself by conquering every stage on each difficulty setting.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🐍 <strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fists First Combat</strong> – Fast-paced Beat ’em Up action with punch combos, finishers, and special moves.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Perfect Parry System</strong> – Time your block just right to deflect attacks <i>and restore health</i>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Finishing Punches</strong> – Deliver flashy knockouts that heal you while sending enemies flying.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro RPG Flavor</strong> – Earn points, tweak your stats, and choose your playstyle in between battles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Two-Player Co-Op</strong> – Grab a friend and take the fight to Morbat City together.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you’ve ever wanted a game that’s equal parts <strong>arcade brawler chaos, RPG progression, and offbeat indie humor</strong> — this is it.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💀 Enemies</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Knuckleheads</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286250/extras/ab03239cd6b58c70b9dd5625d0a74eea.apng?t=1759676943\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286250/extras/ab03239cd6b58c70b9dd5625d0a74eea.poster.avif?t=1759676943\" class=\"bb_img\" width=80 height=80 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286250/extras/48d49d960c9ca00d1a8310809bb7a6ef.webp?t=1759676943\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286250/extras/48d49d960c9ca00d1a8310809bb7a6ef.poster.avif?t=1759676943\" class=\"bb_img\" width=80 height=80 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286250/extras/7a90083cab28a08d4e29967a95407240.apng?t=1759676943\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286250/extras/7a90083cab28a08d4e29967a95407240.poster.avif?t=1759676943\" class=\"bb_img\" width=80 height=80 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286250/extras/4bfab8635c3c5740042426f4bd35c134.apng?t=1759676943\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286250/extras/4bfab8635c3c5740042426f4bd35c134.poster.avif?t=1759676943\" class=\"bb_img\" width=80 height=80 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The bruisers of the Sludge Syndicate, always ready to swarm you in packs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Araneae 1000 a.k.a. &quot;Crawlers&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286250/extras/36b77b29985e7f30283ad072c3febf19.webp?t=1759676943\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286250/extras/36b77b29985e7f30283ad072c3febf19.poster.avif?t=1759676943\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286250/extras/93b3cc121b67a21e84a7845f6bc8c634.poster.avif?t=1759676943\" width=128 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286250/extras/93b3cc121b67a21e84a7845f6bc8c634.webm?t=1759676943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Originally designed as service bots, Crawlers once patrolled Morbat’s streets and assisted in mining operations. Now malfunctioning, they’ve begun rounding up citizens and forcibly taking them...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >📜 <strong>The world as we know it</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Long ago, they were just regular snakes… until they got bitten by radioactive fists - they became Snakes with Fists!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this world, Cobruh and Conduh take on the corrupt <strong>Nexis Corp</strong>, the mega-tech giant tightening its grip on <strong>Morbat City</strong>. With the streets and underground overrun by the ruthless <strong>Sludge Syndicate</strong>, and the outskirts besieged by robotic zealots known as Crawlers, only the Snakes with Fists can stand between the innocent and total chaos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Created by Green Guy Blue Guy</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286250/extras/f34366812d386f6a29ee74b253cec681.avif?t=1759676943\" width=416 height=167 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
